Property

Description

Default

`MaxRetryAttempts`

Maximum number of retry attempts (read-only, set via constructor)

Required

`MillisecondsDelayBetweenRetries`

Base delay between retries (in ms)

0

`BackoffType`

`Constant` or `Exponential` delay

`Constant`

